flowchart TD
    WPE["⚡ wpeframework.service
    Thunder Base Process
    All services Require this"]

    PS["🗄️ persistentstore
    External / Thunder FW
    Independent"]

    WM["🪟 RDKWindowManager
    Independent Provider
    Shell thread · 50ms ready
    No hard deps in suite"]

    OCI["🐳 OCIContainer
    Independent Provider
    Container runtime"]

    SM["📦 AppStorageManager
    Independent Provider
    Storage abstraction"]

    PKG["📋 PackageManagerRDKEMS
    Depends on: AppStorageManager"]

    PRE["🔧 PreinstallManager
    Depends on: PackageManager
    Installs home app"]

    RTM["⚙️ RuntimeManager
    Depends on: AppStorageManager
    OCIContainer · RDKWindowManager
    Ordered after: PreinstallManager"]

    LCM["🔄 LifecycleManager
    Depends on: RuntimeManager
    RDKWindowManager"]

    APM["🚀 AppManager
    Depends on: PersistentStore
    PackageManager
    Ordered after: LifecycleManager"]

    DLM["⬇️ DownloadManager
    Independent
    Ordered after: AppManager"]

    WPE -->|"Requires"| WM
    WPE -->|"Requires"| OCI
    WPE -->|"Requires"| SM
    WPE -->|"Requires (external)"| PS

    WM -.->|"Wants (order only)"| SM

    SM -->|"Requires"| PKG

    PKG -->|"Requires"| PRE

    SM -->|"Requires"| RTM
    WM -->|"Requires"| RTM
    OCI -->|"Requires"| RTM
    PRE -.->|"Wants (order only)"| RTM

    RTM -->|"Requires"| LCM
    WM -->|"Requires"| LCM

    PS -->|"Requires"| APM
    PKG -->|"Requires"| APM
    LCM -.->|"Wants (order only)"| APM

    APM -.->|"Wants (order only)"| DLM

